case 2440
qputs 330 ^32Kibo Ishi
qputs 331 ^12This is an iwakura rock (rock of power) named the Kibo Ishi
qputs 332 ^12(the hope stone). Believed in Shinto religion to house a spirit of
qputs 333 ^12good fortune, many come to make a wish or ask for good luck.
qputs 334 ^12Now a day's many people have begun to throw money into the water
qputs 335 ^12surrounding it like a wishing well before making thier prayer.
