case 2441
qputs 330 ^32100 Year old Sakura Tree
qputs 331 ^12This Sakura tree is 100 years old and is a shinboku, which means
qputs 332 ^12a sacred tree of the Shinto religion.  No one is allowed on the 
qputs 333 ^12small island except Shinto priest or shrine maidens. 
qputs 334 ^12Many pray to this three for protection and to find love.
break
case 2442
qputs 330 ^32Arina Saito 
qputs 331 ^12Here buried is Lady Arina. Guardian of the bamboo forest.
qputs 332 ^12May her sword stand in the heart of the forest and protect 
qputs 333 ^12this place from evil.
break
